data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Assumable Mortgage at 2.75%! You can benefit from the Sellers GREAT RATE!!! Welcome to your dream POOL home, this charming home is ready for you to move in and make it your own.  NEW ROOF, IMPACT WINDOWS, HVAC replaced in 2020, a 50 AMP breaker for your RV and many updates throughout home. This home is ready for YOU!Cute and cozy 3 Bedroom and 2 Bathroom home for first time homebuyers, seasonal, investors or YOUR place in Paradise in the sought after Gardens of Gulf Cove. As you walk through the front door you are greeted by the Living room / Dining combo perfect for entertaining friends and family. The kitchen is bright and features an abundance of soft-closed wood cabinets, spacious counters and stainless steel appliances. The bedrooms are spacious and bright with neutral colors throughout the home so you can make it yours. This home features new vinyl plank flooring throughout the house that offers durability and easy maintenance. The spacious laundry room/utility room is located inside the home. While the large fenced backyard can provide space for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply relaxing in the sunshine, it also comes complete with an oversized outdoor shed with workshop and storage. The screened enclosed pool offers fun and enjoyment all year long with plenty of space for entertaining your family and friends! The Sellers have scheduled to have the pool resurfaced in March! Additionally, the Gardens of Gulf Cove community offers a range of amenities, including swimming pools, tennis courts, and a clubhouse with low HOA. Its proximity to the Gulf of Mexico means that residents can easily enjoy water sports and other outdoor activities. Located just over 9 miles from Englewood Beach, Englewood Hospital, Restaurants, Shopping in many stores both in Englewood and Port Charlotte. Come live in sunny Florida!  This home is ready for YOU!
